description: Uncanny Adventures brings together 30 comic creators from around the world to bring you 21 genre-spanning short stories. From cartoonists just getting their start to established artists presenting their latest works, this collection provides something for every taste. From Victorian horror to science fiction, from autobiographical stories to murder mysteries, Uncanny Adventures showcases the breadth of comics by bringing you tales that will make you think, laugh, and shiver. Featuring a brand new cover by Ethan (Axe Cop) Nicolle.
name: Uncanny Adventures 2013

description:
English digital chapters.

A moving origin story featuring a colorful cast of characters of all shapes, forms and species, each fighting for their place in society. The young Bigoodee embarks on Lady Rozenbilt's extravagant seaplane where high society, criminals and monsters will mingle. This voyage will forever change his life. A complete story that takes place in the same universe as the critically acclaimed District 14, by award-winning authors Gabus and Reutimann.
name: The Fantastic Voyage of Lady Rozenbilt

description:
English digital chapters.

A Sword and Sorcery adventure of a formidable band of mercenaries on a quest for a legendary treasure. At the turbulent period of Christian and Barbarian clashes, a fearsome group of mercenaries reunite after many years apart to take on a secret mission for the Empress of Byzantium. They must search for an infamous treasure hidden in the heart of the ancient underworld. But for all the dangers that lie ahead, both human and supernatural, the greatest one may well rest within them.
name: The Hounds of Hell

deck: One day, Tyler Cross will pay for his crimes.  In the meantime, He's going to commit some more.
description: A gritty 1950s gangster series with the ultimate bad boy of comics in the leading role. Tyler Cross lives his life on a knife edge, but he never shows the slightest sign of losing his cool. Perhaps that’s why he’s one of the most high-in-demand drug traffickers in the USA. With guns, drugs and the occasional explosive, this sexy series with cutting dialogue and dramatic illustration keeps you turning pages right through to the back cover.
name: Tyler Cross

deck: An educational comic that helps friends and relatives deal with people with Alzheimer's Disease
description: The comic panels consists of black and white photographed scenes with word balloons and text boxes inserted in. It also has a few pages of informative text.
name: What Is Happening to Grandpa? A Family Takes Care of a Loved One with Alzheimer's
